                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5793" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0871</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8890 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“肥料大王”靠造假催肥业绩，金正大作茧自缚受重罚</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;Fertilizer King&quot; relies on fraud to increase performance, KINGENTA was caught in a cocoon and severely punished</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">朱清香，苏媛，沈明慧，李小青，许长勇，陈阳阳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金正大生态工程集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金正大；财务舞弊；内部治理；外部治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">KINGENTA; Financial Fraud; Internal Governance; External Governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，上市公司财务舞弊行为层出不穷，严重破环了证券市场的健康发展，引发投资者对资本市场的信任危机。金正大作为我国缓控释肥“第一股”，其复合肥产销量曾连续多年位居国内首位。然而，在2021年5月公司被爆出自2015年起连续五年财务造假，收入虚增金额累计超过230亿元的消息后，其光辉形象轰然倒塌，引起市场一片哗然。本案例以金正大财务舞弊事件为主线，详细描述金正大在被大信会计师事务所出具非标准意见审计报告后，经证监会立案调查，财务舞弊行为暴露的全过程。同时，结合金正大的违法行为跨越了新旧《证券法》适用的特别情形，分析其产生的不利影响。旨在通过对案例的深入解读，引导学生理解并掌握财务舞弊的动因、手段及法律后果，进而从内外部治理角度为我国上市公司财务舞弊行为的防范和监管提出参考性建议。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, financial frauds by listed companies have been emerging constantly, which seriously jeopardize or even disrupt the healthy development of the securities market. Trusts among investors in the capital market have been severely negated. As the first stock of slow/controlled release fertilizers in China, KINGENTA has registered the toppest in the compound fertilizer productions and sales for many consecutive years. However, in May 2021, the news broke out that the company had been committing financial frauds for five consecutive years since 2015. The accumulated increase in revenue have been falsely claimed to exceed 23 billion yuan. It has led directly to the collapse of its “so-glorious” image and touched off a public uproar in the market. The current case study takes KINGENTA’s financial fraud as the main thread to exposit the entire process of this financial fraud exposed by the CSRC after the non-standard opinion audit report issued by the Daxin Certified Public Accountants. At the same time, with reference to the special circumstances that KINGENTA’s illegal activities have crossed-the-line of the old and new &quot;Securities Law&quot;, we analyze the adverse effects it has produced. The aim of the current case study is to guide students to understand the causes, means and legal consequences of financial fraud through in-depth interpretation and exploration of the case. Based on the current case study and from the perspective of internal and external, suggestions are made for the surveillance and prevention of financial frauds by listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》、《商业伦理与会计职业道德》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上市公司财务舞弊、企业或会计师事务所违反职业道德</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
